description: A relentless, driving rain hammers the slick, glistening pavement, each drop a sharp impact. Gusting winds, a mournful howl, tear through sodden, rustling fallen leaves, swirling them in chaotic eddies across the ground. The air is thick with the damp scent of earth and decay, amplifying an anxious atmosphere of profound isolation.
title: My Nightingale Soundscape
